{"tid":1542643,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"社工、輔導人士、老師、心理支援請入","createTime":"2019-09-05T02:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:37:35.000Z","uid":79589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e2100dfe63bc584a62476da6630c94de47345469","tid":1542643,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:15:53.000Z","msg":"現時嘅方法好似都係要等發夢人士主動接觸，先可以幫到佢地做情緒支援<br />\n<br />\n但現時嘅情況可能比想像中更嚴峻<br />\n<br />\n1. 恐怖分子、藍屍搞嘅白色恐怖、批鬥，撕裂哂人同人之間嘅信任<br />\n2. 有好多人家中藍屍主導，迫害子女身心疲憊，但又冇地方宣洩<br />\n<br />\n有冇更加主動、但又安全嘅方式可以幫到佢地？<br />\n<br />\n冇人再想聽到有手足以死明志<br />\n一個都嫌多"},{"pid":"a8b814559671e4796b501f9d98e48fc2764f091e","tid":1542643,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:16:54.000Z","msg":"推10次"},{"pid":"38586020bf44f8b78932cc48718b370a9f49adad","tid":1542643,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:17:18.000Z","msg":"推10次"},{"pid":"f7db9b9ddb0d9a5c9fcd7c92d08e3d6b46dc7081","tid":1542643,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:17:20.000Z","msg":"[正視聽-極重要]唔好再錯focus: 請集中煲五大訴求，還香港高度自治，而唔係執著係咪假withdraw<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542574\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542574</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n- <br />\n幫手推，等美國可以出手做野，要開始打底啦<br />\n如果你keep住講假withdraw,到時星期日佢宣佈撤回，依招你點拆？到時咪又要loop番仲有四個，咁不如依加開始做文宣，仲有幾日時間<br />\n要做到五大訴求or美國制裁<br />\n掉番個波比林鄭"},{"pid":"1d4bdd5a6fd641cef97354aff3e21be1246ef167","tid":1542643,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JN7KNVn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJN7KNVn.jpg&h=50d9f8ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQMGP8H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQMGP8H.jpg&h=8fc5e959&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VC73i13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn